    <string name="uninstall_instructions_title">Uninstalling ABX</string>
    <string name="uninstall_instructions_desc">To fully and permanently remove all data from ABX, simply uninstall the application.\n\nUnder Android\'s File-Based Encryption (FBE) model, all isolated credentials, in-memory states, sandbox files, and log databases are completely and irrecoverably purged from hardware memory upon uninstallation.</string>
    <string name="clear_explanation">You can also manually wipe the security key pair immediately using the button below. This instantly invalidates any currently issued capability tokens and prevents any future authorization checks.</string>
